headline: As Small Business Owners Begin Post-Election Planning for 2025, KeyBank Poll Finds Taxes, Regulations and Trade Policies are Top of Mind
summary: With the election now behind us, many business owners are planning for 2025. A recent KeyBank Small Business Flash Poll found 61% of respondents indicated they were likely to seek clarity and hold off on major business decisions until after the election, while only 12% said the election would have no impact on their 2025 planning.
